creator: Milkish Game Studio
descriptionHtml:
[New update, now with total of 200 Levels!]

Bubur Ayam Rush is a fast-paced cooking food management game from Milkish Game Studio, you'll play as a Chicken porridge seller becoming a World Class Chicken porridge Restaurant! It's FREE and addictive!

Bubur Ayam is one of the most popular dishes in Indonesia. In this game you'll cook porridge, mix it with toppings, and also upgrade and manage your toppings and skills as you progress and serve as many customer as possible!

Fast reflex is what it takes to play this game!
Loads of customers craving for express service in front of your restaurant, cook for them and make them happy! And become the owner of the best chicken porridge restaurant!

Download it now, and get a taste of this unique fast-paced addictive food dash game!

[How to load previous progress from google plus]
Tap on the google play games icon on the top right corner of the title screen, and tap "Cloud Load"

Features:
• a fun cooking & serve game
• Simple, precise fast-paced Tap and Swipe control
• Google achievement
• Google saved games, save can be loaded onto other devices!
• Easy to play, Hard to master!
• Bonus Stage!
• Also get rewards by sharing via Facebook


PERMISSIONS REQUESTED

For more information on our privacy and security policies please see http://www.milkishgames.com/games/bubur-ayam-rush/privacy-policy/

• ACCESS COARSE LOCATION - We use this to optimize ads serving based on the player locations, we do not collect any data for other purposes.

• READ/WRITE EXTERNAL STORAGE - We use this for caching rewarded video ads, and also to store game progress data.
